    The Vehicle class defines an automotive vehicle for this lab. A vehicle is comprised of a String for the model, a VehcileManufacturers for the manufacturer, a double for the number of liters and an Integer for the number of cylinders.       • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Vehicle anotherVehicle)
        The compareTo method ensure that a Vehicle object is passed in and then it compares by the manufacturer enumerated type name. If the names are the same then model is compared. If models are the same then the number of cylinders are compared. Finally, if the cylinders are the same, the number of liters is compared. The entire double value is compared to the other entire double value.
